<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-15687] Regression in traceOutgoingMessage printing message size in tracing</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15687</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The internode messaging refactor (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15066&quot; title=&quot;Improvements to Internode Messaging&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-15066&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-15066&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) introduced a tiny regression to tracing. Previously &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-13028&quot; title=&quot;Log message size in trace message in OutboundTcpConnection&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-13028&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-13028&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; had changed the message emitted by traceOutgoingMessage to include the number of bytes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Sending %s message to %s&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Sending %s message to %s message size %d bytes&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But the change was dropped during the refactor, it&apos;s easy to put it back.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
